	## Commands ##

### Install chart
´´´helm install [name] ./[folder-name]´´´

### Uninstall a chart
´´´helm uninstall [name]

### Information from a chart installed
´´´helm get manifet´´´

### Test Template render befor install
´´´helm install --debug --dry-run [name] ./[folder-name]´´´

### List currentli deploy with helm
´´´helm list´´´
´´´helm list -n [namespace]´´´

## Deployment status
´´´helm status [name] -n [namespace]

## Full information
helm get all [name] -n [namespace]

## Create an emty chart
helm create [emty_chart_name]
